{"tid":841050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿瑞典辱華，內地網民：以後不去IKEA睡覺！","createTime":"2018-09-29T09:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T09:45:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1057f9a3d5e7e35a441ee076f85666f24f8a550d","tid":841050,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"瑞典電視台（SVT）近日在節目「瑞典新聞」播出短片，諷刺中國遊客隨地大便等，結果被內地多個官媒包括央視、新華社、《環球時報》等，紛紛高調譴責辱華，外交部與旅遊部甚至對瑞典發出旅遊警告。不少內地網民揚言要抵制瑞典品牌IKEA，更表示「以後不去IKEA睡覺」。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典時間9月21日晚，當地電視台《瑞典新聞》播出了一段長 1 分 33 秒的影片，內容諷刺早前中國旅客在當地旅館被逐事件，又指中國人隨地大便、不注重清潔、會吃狗肉等。<br />\n<br />\n影片上載至互聯網後，迅速引來中國官方及民間輿論關注，不少人都認為是辱華。隨後大量內地網民湧進內地宜家家居的官方微博留言：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IGxs7-z0xU_GkRWxJFUNlWXbiZiIXqBkpenB9aXpwfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2FIGxs7-z0xU_GkRWxJFUNlWXbiZiIXqBkpenB9aXpwfU.jpg&h=5606e481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「瑞典國實在是太壞了，我們決定再也不去宜家買東西了，那樣瑞典國明天就破了」、「抵制瑞典以後再也不去宜家睡覺」、「昨天還想在宜家買點東西，今天果斷放棄」、「好好活著不好嗎？還敢公開辱華，是沒見識過中國人的團結一致，共抗外敵？」<br />\n<br />\n當然，也有心水清的網民指出，IKEA在中國賣的商品，有80%都是中國製造。根據資料，IKEA在中國的供貨商多達 370 間，替宜家加工的工廠則逾 200 間，當中約 80% 貨物主要供應給中國，全球商品中中國製造的僅佔 15%，換句話說，在中國製的商品，其實大部份生產完就直接入商場，因此一旦抵制宜家，中國工人就失業了。"},{"pid":"00382f5500189d36564ca940ec168249fbe2c86d","tid":841050,"uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"Ikea成最後贏家"},{"pid":"91748623feddffc36ab4cbdbe7a2bacf1330b372","tid":841050,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"中国又贏！"},{"pid":"48f915e028e9f40a9ab92f4c61b2e5e4171ff077","tid":841050,"uid":78470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">換句話說，在中國製的商品，其實大部份生產完就直接入商場，因此一旦抵制宜家，中國工人就失業了。</span><br />\n又自己人打自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ea2129ed1cc65fdf39f6099a7c7e57fd057634","tid":841050,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"宜家變到乾淨曬又安靜環境又好，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4556de0c389f1948a24aaa0ef47cd3f5ca20909f","tid":841050,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad8df1dcf8605915c801f24492b2e0d46cbfe57","tid":841050,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"今次ikea真係感激萬分 少左蟲訓污糟d床"},{"pid":"b531fbee0e8660866fdf874c05db3c7b163a3019","tid":841050,"uid":41992,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"唔去IKEA訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解佢地會講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9451becfd095f72a9c9f5e153edec9fbcd60677","tid":841050,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"即係叫人繼續侮辱你姐"},{"pid":"16bed8cd1afab3d99a8f40eddb52e5ff9519fc9f","tid":841050,"uid":1248,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"唯一一個識曲線自嘲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}